title: High School girls’ volleyball: Philipsburg-Osecola takes down Central Mountain in five sets
text:
Published By: Centre Daily Times - Yesterday 
Behind an eight-kill, four-ace, two-block night from Cheyenne Bone, Philipsburg-Osceola outlasted Central Mountain 25-20, 25-20, 15-25, 20-2...
